column5: Just wanted to see if anyone was heading to simco tomorrow i just had my brother in-law back out so that leaves me fishing alone. Wanted to see if any other OFC members would out tomorrow.

CoLD, with a nice breeze out of the NW.  It sounds like a day that you could boast about, whether you catch or not.  I think I will bake some bread instead.  And maybe some beef stew to go along with.  Looking to the future, AileGoby, you might be able to cruise by my place next time on your way to the laker/perch holes.  I pay for gas and minnows, and, as always, the gweeches are on me.
sounds good douG  If anyone plans on going hit me up. It my be cold out but in the hut i'll be cooking at 18,000 BTUs if that helps lol
Hope you rock em, tight lines.
Jigger in the AM not the PM sorry about that
I will be out there. I live in Barrie and my hut is in Shanty bay.  I would offer you a spot in it but my fishing partner is coming out.
Thanks Cudz plans just changed again hitting the Bog tomorrow with Jigger Thanks for the offer
